==============================================================================
DeepSeek Chat - Language File
==============================================================================
Structure:
  ID   1-100  : System messages (errors, status, confirmations)
  ID 101-200  : Settings panel texts
  ID 201-300  : Chat interface texts (buttons, labels, placeholders)

Placeholder syntax: {0}, {1}, {2} for dynamic values

Languages:
  en     : English  (default)
  de     : Deutsch
  es     : Español
  custom : User-defined language (visible only when populated)
           Pre-filled with English as fallback.
           To activate: set visible="true" and replace texts with your language.

Adding a new language:
  1. Copy the <language id="custom" ...> block
  2. Set a new unique id (e.g. id="fr")
  3. Set visible="true"
  4. Set name to the display name (e.g. "Français")
  5. Translate all <text> elements
==============================================================================
-->
